<D>__{scalpel! no... no... a larger one... the largest we have!}
<A>__{she slaps a huge one into his palm. he takes a deep breath and goes to work. masked heads gather round him. the scalpel is poised at the line where skin meets steel. we make an incision. the instruments go crazy. warning bells and buzzers sound.}
<C>__{head nurse}
<D>__{kill the alarms!}
